             were indicted for <rs id="t18240715-113-off605" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18240715-113-off605" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18240715-113-off605" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18240715-113-cd606" type="crimeDate">16th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18240715-113-off605 t18240715-113-cd606"></join>, a handkerchief, value 2 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18240715-113-victim1022" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Godwin
                        <interp inst="t18240715-113-victim1022" type="surname" value="Godwin"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18240715-113-victim1022" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
